<HEAD>Army Says 21 Bodies Found Over Weekend Were Tortured, Strangled</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By ALFONSO ANZUETO</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>GUATEMALA CITY, Guatemala (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
