</TEXT>
<TEXT>
 Section 11 The federal, state or local authorities of the <LOCATION> United </LOCATION> <LOCATION> States </LOCATION> shall not impose any impediments to transit to or from the headquarters district of representatives of members or officials of the <ORGANIZATION> United </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Nations </ORGANIZATION>, or of specialized agencies -LRB- or -RRB- representatives of nongovernmental organizations recognized by the <ORGANIZATION> United </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Nations </ORGANIZATION> for the for the purpose of consultation.
