<PERSON> Feinberg </PERSON> and <ORGANIZATION> University </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Virginia </ORGANIZATION> law professor <PERSON> Stephen </PERSON> <PERSON> A. </PERSON> <PERSON> Saltzburg </PERSON>, will nominate successors. The nominations are subject to approval by <PERSON> Merhige </PERSON>. <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Sheppard </PERSON>, director of the trust's claims resolution facility, said the trust's bylaws will be amended to permit a quorum of two trustees to conduct business. `` We expect no slowdown,'' <PERSON> Sheppard </PERSON> said.
